  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n  <strong>Note:</strong> please note that Liferay has renamed its Liferay Experience\n  Could offerings to <i><strong>Liferay SaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC) and\n  <i><strong>Liferay PaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC-SM).\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HYXPGNHPH0ACA1CSRJ9E4W6N\">Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Modify existing service account to handle db export/import</li>\n<li>Implement GCS Backup Create Strategy</li>\n<li>Create mechanism to switch doclib format for a given project</li>\n<li>Build client extensions in service-jenkins</li>\n<li> Detect if Liferay PaaS Extension needs the Extension Init Metadata volume mount</li>\n<li>VPN 1/2: make unit tests the majority of test coverage, surpassing integration tests in number and ease of use</li>\n<li>Add terms of service to the login page</li>\n<li>Add latest login timestamp column to the teams page</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HYXPGNHQGZKR161KV3TPHET5\">Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add 'application/javascript' mime/type to the list of valid gzip files</li>\n<li>Install build-essential on Jenkins service</li>\n<li>Fixed quthentication errors on database service</li>\n<li>Fixed 404 page is unstyled</li>\n<li>Fixed backup service crashes and restarts when connected to external project</li>\n<li>Getting error 502 when send a request for autoscaling route</li>\n<li>Failed to run CI Job for Liferay-DXP service</li>\n<li>Create secret page does not allow creation of some secrets needed for services stack</li>\n<li>Duplicate key error on updating service env var</li>\n<li>Dynatrace Provisioning must be enabled by default</li>\n<li>SPA is broken for new console pages</li>\n<li>Users with SRE role are not able to load some pages on Console</li>\n<li>Update VPN documentation link</li>\n<li>Fix migration guide link on cloud console</li>\n<li>Admin client does not show provisioning entries</li>\n</ul>"
      },
